523
00:38:06,855 --> 00:38:10,192
Tell him you were afraid of love,
afraid of needing.

524
00:38:10,192 --> 00:38:13,028
- Needing what?
- To belong to someone.

525
00:38:13,028 --> 00:38:15,197
We all are, sweetheart.

526
00:38:15,197 --> 00:38:17,866
I'm sorry about that.

527
00:38:17,866 --> 00:38:23,438
Tell him this is the worst, cruelest,
dumbest moment to do this to him...

528
00:38:23,438 --> 00:38:25,374
