- Good. So do I.

552
00:40:11,480 --> 00:40:14,074
So sometimes--

553
00:40:16,651 --> 00:40:18,118
could you excuse us?

554
00:40:23,492 --> 00:40:25,026
Sometimes...

555
00:40:25,026 --> 00:40:27,662
