566
00:41:18,246 --> 00:41:20,510
What's he doing here?
You working this weekend?

567
00:41:24,219 --> 00:41:27,814
- He's here to be with me.
- Why?

568
00:41:29,224 --> 00:41:34,396
Because he's my friend.
He's my good friend.

569
00:41:34,396 --> 00:41:35,988
My best friend these days.

570
00:41:39,568 --> 00:41:41,729
