- For one day find me irresistible.

585
00:43:04,219 --> 00:43:05,652
Stop it.

586
00:43:09,991 --> 00:43:11,788
Is something wrong?

587
00:43:14,162 --> 00:43:17,766
I guess it's just the way
you've always talked about George.

588
00:43:17,766 --> 00:43:21,302
It always seemed...

589
00:43:21,302 --> 00:43:24,005
seemed like--

590
00:43:24,005 --> 00:43:27,942
