597
00:43:54,536 --> 00:43:57,138
Indeed.
Worked for me.

598
00:43:57,138 --> 00:43:58,628
Big time.

599
00:44:02,711 --> 00:44:04,872
Right.

600
00:44:10,385 --> 00:44:12,819
Oh, my God.
Race you to the altar.

601
00:44:14,055 --> 00:44:16,124
- Underplay.
- Got it.

602
00:44:16,124 --> 00:44:18,226
I'm Jules' fiance, George.

603
00:44:18,226 --> 00:44:22,564
Just in town for a quick pre-conjugal
visit, it you catch my drift.

604
00:44:22,564 --> 00:44:23,997
