605
00:44:25,233 --> 00:44:27,736
- You're going to humiliate me.
- Only if I can.

606
00:44:27,736 --> 00:44:30,371
Just one thing.
Stay away from--

607
00:44:30,371 --> 00:44:32,999
George! Oh, my God!

608
00:44:35,410 --> 00:44:39,748
- I don't know why I'm so carried away.
- Me neither.

609
00:44:39,748 --> 00:44:41,181
It's so--

610
00:44:42,917 --> 00:44:44,919
Against God's plan?

611
00:44:44,919 --> 00:44:47,889
No! It's just wonderful !

612
00:44:47,889 --> 00:44:50,187
It's so wonderful!

613
00:44:54,262 --> 00:44:55,695
Mom!

614
00:44:59,601 --> 00:45:03,104
- What?
- You have to meet George.

615
00:45:03,104 --> 00:45:05,607
You must be
Kimmy's little sister.

616
00:45:05,607 --> 00:45:09,210
Julianne's fiance.
They're going to be married.

617
00:45:09,210 --> 00:45:11,446
- What's going on?
- Julianne's getting married.

618
00:45:11,446 --> 00:45:13,982
- Why didn't you tell us?
- There hasn't been time.

619
00:45:13,982 --> 00:45:17,452
I wanted to. I wanted
to shout it from the rooftops...

620
00:45:17,452 --> 00:45:21,122
