''No, Pumpkin, no.

621
00:45:21,122 --> 00:45:22,624
This is Kimmy's day.

622
00:45:22,624 --> 00:45:25,058
Let's not take the attention
away from Kimmy.

623
00:45:26,127 --> 00:45:28,129
Dear, sweet...

624
00:45:28,129 --> 00:45:30,757
adorable,
chocolate-covered Kimmy.''

625
00:45:31,633 --> 00:45:34,402
