we'd end up like this:

674
00:48:19,300 --> 00:48:22,136
like some glittering...

675
00:48:22,136 --> 00:48:25,936
Doris Day-Rock Hudson
extravaganza.

676
00:48:27,575 --> 00:48:29,077
l said to Dionne...

677
00:48:29,077 --> 00:48:32,480
''Dionne, I'm in love.

678
00:48:32,480 --> 00:48:35,316
Could this siren love me?

679
00:48:35,316 --> 00:48:38,152
Are the gods that kind?''

680
00:48:38,152 --> 00:48:43,590
And Dionne turned to me,
opened her lovely eyes and said...

681
00:48:50,198 --> 00:48:51,756
What did she say?

682
00:48:54,168 --> 00:48:56,329
The moment I wake up

683
00:48:59,440 --> 00:49:02,377
Before I put on my makeup

684
00:49:02,377 --> 00:49:05,642
