685
00:49:07,715 --> 00:49:10,183
While combing my hair now

686
00:49:11,686 --> 00:49:14,789
While wondering
what dress to wear now

687
00:49:14,789 --> 00:49:18,359
I say a little prayer for you

688
00:49:18,359 --> 00:49:21,963
Forever and ever
you'll stay in my heart

689
00:49:21,963 --> 00:49:23,631
And I will love you

690
00:49:23,631 --> 00:49:26,534
Forever and ever
We never will part

691
00:49:26,534 --> 00:49:28,036
Oh, how I love you

692
00:49:28,036 --> 00:49:31,039
Together forever
That's how it must be

693
00:49:31,039 --> 00:49:34,075
To live without you
would only mean

694
00:49:34,075 --> 00:49:36,811
Heartbreak for me

695
00:49:36,811 --> 00:49:38,972
Go, Granddaddy!

696
00:49:40,882 --> 00:49:43,373
l run for the bus, dear

697
00:49:44,485 --> 00:49:47,852
While riding
l think of us, dear

698
00:49:52,060 --> 00:49:54,221
At work I just take time

699
00:49:55,329 --> 00:49:58,492
And all through
my coffee break time

700
00:50:21,189 --> 00:50:23,521
My darling, believe me

701
00:50:24,759 --> 00:50:30,459
For me there is no one but you

702
00:50:31,566 --> 00:50:35,069
- Please love me too
- Answer his prayer

703
00:50:35,069 --> 00:50:38,106
- And I'm in love with you
- Answer his prayer now

704
00:50:38,106 --> 00:50:40,199
Answer my prayer, baby

705
00:50:41,442 --> 00:50:44,036
Say you love me too

706
00:51:08,002 --> 00:51:10,436
all right, now!

707
00:51:12,473 --> 00:51:15,143
- Heartbreak for you, actually.
- You've made your point.

708
00:51:15,143 --> 00:51:20,513
Get on your plane. I'll call at the turn
of the century when I've forgiven you.

709
00:51:22,817 --> 00:51:26,320
- It never would have worked out.
