710
00:51:26,320 --> 00:51:27,810
Different temperaments.

711
00:51:30,825 --> 00:51:33,692
Look, tell him you love him.

712
00:51:34,996 --> 00:51:36,930
Bite the bullet.

713
00:51:48,176 --> 00:51:50,011
