714
00:51:50,011 --> 00:51:51,945
''Be Careful
Watch Your Step''

715
00:51:59,187 --> 00:52:01,856
He'll choose Kim.

716
00:52:01,856 --> 00:52:04,792
You'll stand beside her
at the wedding...

717
00:52:04,792 --> 00:52:07,955
