721
00:52:35,056 --> 00:52:36,857
It's been over for ages...

722
00:52:36,857 --> 00:52:39,060
but he can't accept it.

723
00:52:39,060 --> 00:52:41,896
I'd built you up so much...

724
00:52:41,896 --> 00:52:45,166
l couldn't let him lose face
in front of you.

725
00:52:45,166 --> 00:52:50,661
