737
00:54:21,529 --> 00:54:24,760
- There are a lot of memories.
- It's more than that.

738
00:54:27,301 --> 00:54:31,260
It's kind of embarrassing
to say it this way, but...

739
00:54:32,807 --> 00:54:35,910
you've sort of been,
you know...

740
00:54:35,910 --> 00:54:38,572
the woman in my life.

741
00:54:40,481 --> 00:54:43,551
You've been the man in mine.

742
00:54:43,551 --> 00:54:46,620
And I was thinking
this could be our last time...

